---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="Best Tattoo Studio Software 2026 — Top 5 Compared | InkFlow" description="We compared the best tattoo studio software: InkFlow vs Booksy vs Vagaro vs DaySmart vs Tattoo Studio Pro. Features, pricing, and who should use what." />
  <Navbar />

  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-3">BUYER'S GUIDE 2026</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">Best Tattoo Studio Software 2026</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Choosing the right platform is one of the biggest decisions for your studio. We compared the top 5 options — features, pricing, and who each one is best for.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QUICK PICK -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-12 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-accent-400 font-semibold">🏆 OUR TOP PICK</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white">InkFlow — Best All-in-One for Tattoo Studios</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400">Only platform built specifically for tattoo studios with booking, waivers, CRM, payments, aftercare, and inventory — all included. <strong class="text-white">Free plan available.</strong></p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try Free →</a>
        <a href="#comparison" class="inline-block rounded-lg border border-ink-700 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white hover:bg-ink-800 transition-all">See Full Comparison ↓</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW TO CHOOSE -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">How to Choose the Right Software</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Before diving into the comparison, ask yourself these 3 questions:</p>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-5"><p class="text-white font-medium">1. How many artists are in your studio?</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Solo artists have different needs than multi-artist shops. Some platforms charge per artist — the costs add up fast.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-5"><p class="text-white font-medium">2. Do you need digital waivers?</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Many booking platforms don't include waivers. You'd pay extra for a separate waiver app like Waiverly or Smartwaiver.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-5"><p class="text-white font-medium">3. What's your budget?</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Prices range from free to $349/mo. Consider the total cost: booking + waivers + SMS + payments + commission tracking.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FULL COMPARISON TABLE -->
  <section id="comparison" class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Feature Comparison</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-gray-400">
          <thead class="text-left text-xs uppercase text-gray-500">
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800">
              <th class="pb-4 pr-4 font-medium">Feature</th>
              <th class="pb-4 pr-4 font-medium text-accent-400">InkFlow</th>
              <th class="pb-4 pr-4 font-medium">Booksy</th>
              <th class="pb-4 pr-4 font-medium">Vagaro</th>
              <th class="pb-4 pr-4 font-medium">DaySmart</th>
              <th class="pb-4 font-medium">TSP</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-ink-800/50">
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Online Booking</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✅</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅</td><td class="py-3">✅</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Digital Waivers</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">Built-in</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅</td><td class="py-3">✅</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Client CRM</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">360°</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">Basic</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅</td><td class="py-3">Basic</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Commission Tracking</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">Auto</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">Manual</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅</td><td class="py-3">❌</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Aftercare Automation</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✅</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌</td><td class="py-3">❌</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Inventory Tracking</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✅</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">Basic</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅</td><td class="py-3">❌</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Tattoo-Specific</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✅ Built for</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌ Salon</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">⚠️ Salon</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">✅ Built for</td><td class="py-3">✅ Built for</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">SMS Reminders Cost</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">Included</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">$0.07/msg</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">Included</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">Included</td><td class="py-3">Included</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Free Plan</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✅ $0/mo</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">⚠️ Limited</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">❌</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">14-day trial</td><td class="py-3">30-day trial</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-white">Starting Price</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400 font-medium">$0/mo</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">$29.99/mo</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">$35/mo</td><td class="py-3 pr-4">~$33/mo</td><td class="py-3">~$35/mo</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PLATFORM BREAKDOWNS -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Platform Breakdowns</h2>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-accent-500/30 bg-accent-500/5 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">🥇 InkFlow — Best Overall for Tattoo Studios</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">The only platform built from the ground up for tattoo studios. Includes booking, digital waivers, CRM, payment processing, commission tracking, aftercare automation, and inventory — all in one system.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm"><span class="text-green-400">Best for:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Solo artists to multi-artist studios who want an all-in-one solution with a free plan.</span></p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm"><span class="text-yellow-400">Trade-off:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Newer platform — fewer third-party integrations than mature competitors.</span></p>
        <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm text-accent-400 hover:underline">Start Free →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Booksy</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">General booking platform popular in beauty/salon. Good for client discovery through their marketplace. No tattoo-specific features — no waivers, commission tracking, or aftercare.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm"><span class="text-green-400">Best for:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Studios that rely on Booksy marketplace for new client acquisition.</span></p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm"><span class="text-yellow-400">Trade-off:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">No waivers ($30-80/mo extra through third-party), no commission tracking, SMS costs extra.</span></p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Vagaro</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">Feature-rich salon software with booking, POS, and marketing. Strong for multi-location studios. Not tattoo-specific — no built-in waivers or aftercare automation.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm"><span class="text-green-400">Best for:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Larger studios that need marketing tools and multi-location support.</span></p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm"><span class="text-yellow-400">Trade-off:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Expensive for small teams, no tattoo-specific features, no free plan.</span></p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">DaySmart Body Art (formerly InkBook)</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">Mature tattoo-specific platform with scheduling, waivers, POS, inventory, and payroll. Strong on compliance. Mobile apps available but web interface shows its age.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm"><span class="text-green-400">Best for:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Established studios that need robust payroll and inventory management.</span></p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm"><span class="text-yellow-400">Trade-off:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Older interface, no free plan, limited modern features (aftercare automation, AI).</span></p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Tattoo Studio Pro (TSP)</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">Popular mobile-first tattoo management app with booking, waivers, and Stripe POS. Good for solo to small shops. Limited CRM, no aftercare automation, no inventory tracking.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm"><span class="text-green-400">Best for:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Solo artists who want a simple mobile booking + waiver solution.</span></p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm"><span class="text-yellow-400">Trade-off:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">No desktop web app, limited client management, no aftercare.</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHEN TO PICK WHAT -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Quick Decision Guide</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20"><span class="text-sm text-accent-400">→</span></div><div><p class="text-white font-medium">Solo artist on a budget</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">InkFlow Free or Goldie. Both have free plans with booking + deposits.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20"><span class="text-sm text-accent-400">→</span></div><div><p class="text-white font-medium">Growing studio (2-5 artists)</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">InkFlow or TSP. Multi-artist support with commission tracking and waivers built in.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20"><span class="text-sm text-accent-400">→</span></div><div><p class="text-white font-medium">Large studio with payroll needs</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">DaySmart Body Art. Mature payroll and QuickBooks integration.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20"><span class="text-sm text-accent-400">→</span></div><div><p class="text-white font-medium">Multi-location with marketing focus</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Vagaro or InkFlow. InkFlow is catching up on marketing features but at lower cost.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">What is the best tattoo studio software for solo artists?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">InkFlow (free plan) or Goldie. Both offer booking, deposits, and reminders at $0/month. InkFlow adds digital waivers and CRM even on the free plan.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Which platform has the best tattoo waiver features?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">InkFlow and DaySmart Body Art both include built-in digital waivers. InkFlow's waivers integrate with booking and client profiles — no extra fee.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Is free tattoo studio software any good?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Yes — InkFlow's free plan includes booking, waivers, CRM, and reminders. It's not a stripped trial — it's a fully functional plan for solo artists.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Try the Best Tattoo Studio Software Free</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400">No credit card. No time limit on the free plan.</p>
    <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-10 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Start Free →</a>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600">Also see: <a href="/compare/booksy" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">InkFlow vs Booksy</a> · <a href="/compare/tattoo-studio-pro" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">vs Tattoo Studio Pro</a> · <a href="/pricing" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">Pricing</a></p>
  </section>
